__TableColumn__.expression: CASE WHEN dod_earliest is not NULL THEN 'Ambiguous DOD' end
CASE WHEN DOB is NULL THEN 'Missing DOB' end
CASE WHEN race LIKE '%,%' THEN 'Ambiguous Race' End
CASE WHEN sex LIKE '%,%' THEN 'Ambiguous Sex'  End
CASE WHEN dob_latest is not NULL THEN 'Ambiguous DOB' end

CASE WHEN 
    dod_earliest is not NULL
    OR dob_latest is not NULL
    OR sex LIKE '%,%'
    OR race LIKE '%,%'
    THEN 'Ambiguous' 
  WHEN  dob is NULL THEN 'Missing DOB'
  ELSE 'Consistent' END

__SqlMetric__.expression:
(#(hll_union_agg(bene_hll) FILTER (
        WHERE consistent_dob = 'CONSISTENT'
        AND consistent_dod <> 'AMBIGUOUS'
        AND consistent_race = 'CONSISTENT'
        AND consistent_sex = 'CONSISTENT'
        ))
        ) * 100.0 / (#(hll_union_agg(bene_hll)))
